  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >From pilots with no real-life experience to experienced pilots who want to improve their skills, <strong><i>Uncrashed</i></strong> will provide you the opportunity to fly FPV drones in a beautiful, realistic simulator.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Take the race to the next level without risking breaking your drone or your bank account.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1682970/extras/58b070ae5e1a9c96dc985a12322a07fc.poster.avif?t=1767873147\" width=600 height=178 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1682970/extras/58b070ae5e1a9c96dc985a12322a07fc.webm?t=1767873147\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1682970/extras/58b070ae5e1a9c96dc985a12322a07fc.mp4?t=1767873147\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >MULTIPLAYER</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Explore the skies alongside fellow players, dive into competitive races with friends, or strive for dominance on the leaderboards. Multiplayer transforms training into a captivating and thrilling adventure!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >MANY BIG MAPS</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Whether it's for freestyle or race training, the many large and diverse maps have been designed by a team with extensive FPV knowledge to give you a better flying experience. From parks to the best abandoned places, you have never seen such beautiful spots for FPV drones.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >ENVIRONMENT & TRACK EDITOR</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Create your own environment, your own races or take advantage of the thousands of community creations.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >CUSTOMIZATION</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>EASY TO USE SETTINGS</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Simple settings, based on real values will allow you to easily reproduce your own drone.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1682970/extras/30b23b8c8df87482d2e577deda811b9a.poster.avif?t=1767873147\" width=600 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1682970/extras/30b23b8c8df87482d2e577deda811b9a.webm?t=1767873147\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1682970/extras/30b23b8c8df87482d2e577deda811b9a.mp4?t=1767873147\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>FOR MORE ADVANCED USER</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You can even fine-tune physics settings like gravity, air friction or even propeller efficiency depending on the throttle level.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1682970/extras/383c8df7f5e374503588f6a278d281cf.poster.avif?t=1767873147\" width=600 height=178 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1682970/extras/383c8df7f5e374503588f6a278d281cf.webm?t=1767873147\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1682970/extras/383c8df7f5e374503588f6a278d281cf.mp4?t=1767873147\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Any Joystick/gamepad recognized by Windows will work, but a radio-controller is highly recommended.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Support for PC-compatible radio-controller.</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >From pilots with no real-life experience to experienced pilots who want to improve their skills, <strong><i>Uncrashed</i></strong> will provide you the opportunity to fly FPV drones in a beautiful, realistic simulator.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Take the race to the next level without risking breaking your drone or your bank account.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1682970/extras/58b070ae5e1a9c96dc985a12322a07fc.poster.avif?t=1767873147\" width=600 height=178 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1682970/extras/58b070ae5e1a9c96dc985a12322a07fc.webm?t=1767873147\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1682970/extras/58b070ae5e1a9c96dc985a12322a07fc.mp4?t=1767873147\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >MULTIPLAYER</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Explore the skies alongside fellow players, dive into competitive races with friends, or strive for dominance on the leaderboards. Multiplayer transforms training into a captivating and thrilling adventure!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >MANY BIG MAPS</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Whether it's for freestyle or race training, the many large and diverse maps have been designed by a team with extensive FPV knowledge to give you a better flying experience. From parks to the best abandoned places, you have never seen such beautiful spots for FPV drones.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >ENVIRONMENT & TRACK EDITOR</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Create your own environment, your own races or take advantage of the thousands of community creations.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >CUSTOMIZATION</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>EASY TO USE SETTINGS</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Simple settings, based on real values will allow you to easily reproduce your own drone.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1682970/extras/30b23b8c8df87482d2e577deda811b9a.poster.avif?t=1767873147\" width=600 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1682970/extras/30b23b8c8df87482d2e577deda811b9a.webm?t=1767873147\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1682970/extras/30b23b8c8df87482d2e577deda811b9a.mp4?t=1767873147\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>FOR MORE ADVANCED USER</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You can even fine-tune physics settings like gravity, air friction or even propeller efficiency depending on the throttle level.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1682970/extras/383c8df7f5e374503588f6a278d281cf.poster.avif?t=1767873147\" width=600 height=178 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1682970/extras/383c8df7f5e374503588f6a278d281cf.webm?t=1767873147\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1682970/extras/383c8df7f5e374503588f6a278d281cf.mp4?t=1767873147\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Any Joystick/gamepad recognized by Windows will work, but a radio-controller is highly recommended.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Support for PC-compatible radio-controller.</p>",
